    Copied! 
    ckpt = torch.load(model_path)
model = pSp(ckpt).to("cuda")


def generate(img: Arr32F) -> Arr32F:
    pil_img = Image.fromarray(img, mode="F")
    input_img = transform(pil_img).unsqueeze(0).to("cuda")
    output_img = model.forward(input_img, "generate", disable_noise=True)[0][0][0]
    return output_img.detach().cpu().numpy()
    ckpt = torch.load(model_path) model = pSp(ckpt).to("cuda") def generate(img: Arr32F) -> Arr32F: pil_img = Image.fromarray(img, mode="F") input_img = transform(pil_img).unsqueeze(0).to("cuda") output_img = model.forward(input_img, "generate", disable_noise=True)[0][0][0] return output_img.detach().cpu().numpy()
